{"tid":673781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律師料判囚4年多","createTime":"2018-05-22T06:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T09:07:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"202996e62f6ca25330c60ca00319896979952635","tid":673781,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:47:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180522/20398208\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180522%2F20398208&d=l5eGLvVAMMxnCWCHCGEdVP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=5bb9e7be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180522%2F20398208&h=7dfcc178\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180522/20398208</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018年05月22日 <br />\n<br />\n律師料判囚4年多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180522/large/a0203a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180522%2Flarge%2Fa0203a.gif&h=294f03a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁天琦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】旺角騷亂歷時近12小時，至少103名警員受傷，91人被捕，過去一年法庭已審結3宗暴動案，判刑由判入教導所至監禁4年9個月不等；梁天琦判刑如何，備受關注。有律師估計，由於梁的煽惑暴動罪不成立，「唔可以話佢係mastermind（主腦）」，估計判刑大概4年多，「暴動最高刑罰係10年，係咪要留啲空間畀更加大鑊嘅嘢？」<br />\n<br />\n律師林偉展接受《蘋果》查詢，指環顧中外暴動事件，旺角騷亂以嚴重性而言，「只算係中至輕嘅暴動」，也遠遠及不上六七暴動。旺角騷亂至今判刑最重一案的被告，是將起火紙皮箱拉到一輛的士旁邊，最終因暴動及縱火罪入獄4年9個月，律師指縱火較襲警嚴重，故梁判刑應較輕。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，港英政府因應六七暴動，於1970年制訂《公安條例》，當中加入暴動罪，其後用於檢控在越南船民營等參與暴動人士。至旺角騷亂，被控暴動人數20多人，明日將有10人判刑，不計梁案共3人或須重審，另外尚有兩人候審。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁偉強  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n另一被告經歷傘運對警有偏見<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n李柱銘：政府最應該負責<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官以強姦犯為例：判刑可考慮案件背景<br />\n<br />\n求情信指天琦天性善良聞子在囚仍樂於助人　梁父熱淚盈眶<br />\n<br />\n另一被告經歷傘運對警有偏見<br />\n<br />\n李柱銘：政府最應該負責<br />\n<br />\n炮轟騷亂　陳婉嫻：六七暴動為貧苦大眾<br />\n<br />\n嘆自己一代貪圖逸樂令民主倒退大狀讚梁天琦　勇於承擔　不放棄香港"},{"pid":"151f3008f44e520a5b42a59be25e2ffdbd4daf15","tid":673781,"uid":123711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:47:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e63aa874e48a555f625816577f4c64305ad1fe85","tid":673781,"uid":36296,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:48:04.000Z","msg":"4年冇人記得佢地Lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef2c5f4f13caac07a371fbcf73f86bcad9a3914","tid":673781,"uid":102096,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:55:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86201d7337c58386aceb7aa5f4c9ca8b6dee75fe","tid":673781,"uid":42804,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1ef2c5f4f13caac07a371fbcf73f86bcad9a3914","tid":673781,"uid":102096,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:55:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:14:10.000Z","msg":"五毛直頭想佢變成第二個劉曉波。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fdcb3f0bbfe3c1371d6a4b52d59bb53c782b909","tid":673781,"uid":4525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:17:09.000Z","msg":"入到去又可以繼續讀書"},{"pid":"38a52c29eb0af6e84734ca5a23639667d6f9a505","tid":673781,"uid":42804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7fdcb3f0bbfe3c1371d6a4b52d59bb53c782b909","tid":673781,"uid":4525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:17:09.000Z","msg":"入到去又可以繼續讀書"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:32:25.000Z","msg":"一向都可以，不過問題係坐完之後，出來社會係點另一回事。<br />\n而家咁嘅情況，應該擔心嘅會唔會獄中被自殺。"},{"pid":"ad908e18e2f62a767297af0dbaeefc9d333c6bdd","tid":673781,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T08:16:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"564c5f33a8058f66ea3e83e2362fbf69de98d9f4","tid":673781,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T08:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/